OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSchools bewildered by AI   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fadvances, say heads        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, UK schools have been left confused by  
OL,6, the fast rate of change in artificial  
OL,7, intelligence (AI) and its impact on    
OL,8, education, head teachers are warning.  
OL,10,FIn a letter to the Times, educators    
OL,11,Ffrom the state and private sector say  
OL,12,Fdevelopments are "bewildering".        
OL,14,FThey are launching a body of experts to
OL,15,Fadvise schools on which areas are      
OL,16,F"beneficial, and which are damaging".  
OL,18,FThe technology is moving "far too      
OL,19,Fquickly" for government alone to give  
OL,20,Fadequate advice to schools, they say.  
